      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • editor

          javax.swing.JTextArea editor

        • openedFilePath

          java.nio.file.Path openedFilePath

        • copiedText

          java.lang.String copiedText

        • flp

          FormLocalizationProvider flp

          java.util.List<E> buttonList

          boolean modified

        • toolBar

          LJToolBar toolBar

        • newDocumentAction

          javax.swing.Action newDocumentAction
          Method used to define the action for the "New" menu option. It opens a new file and lets the user save the old one if it had been changed since the last save.

        • openDocumentAction

          javax.swing.Action openDocumentAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Open" menu option. It lets the user open another file and lets the user save the old one if it had been changed since the last save.

        • saveDocumentAction

          javax.swing.Action saveDocumentAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Save" menu option. It lets the user save the current file. If the file name has been defined it simply overrides the old file, if it hasn't the method asks the user to define the name and the location of the file.

        • saveAsDocumentAction

          javax.swing.Action saveAsDocumentAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Save As" menu option. It lets the user save the current file to the desired location and with desired name.

        • cutSelectedPartAction

          javax.swing.Action cutSelectedPartAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Cut" menu option. It lets the user copy a part of the text and delete it from the text area.

        • copySelectedPartAction

          javax.swing.Action copySelectedPartAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Copy" menu option. It lets the user copy a part of the text.

        • pasteSelectedPartAction

          javax.swing.Action pasteSelectedPartAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Paste" menu option. It lets the user paste the previously copied text to the desired location. User can also select a part of the text and paste the copied text over it. This will remove the selected text.

        • deleteSelectedPartAction

          javax.swing.Action deleteSelectedPartAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Delete" menu option. It lets the user delete the selected part of the text.

        • toggleCaseAction

          javax.swing.Action toggleCaseAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Toggle Case" menu option. It lets the user switch the Case of the selected text. If no text is selected the whole text will switch Case.

        • englishLanguageAction

          javax.swing.Action englishLanguageAction
          Method used set the current localization language to english.

        • croatianLanguageAction

          javax.swing.Action croatianLanguageAction
          Method used set the current localization language to croatian.

        • exitAction

          javax.swing.Action exitAction
          Method used to define the action for the "Exit" menu option. If the file has changed since the last save it lets the user save it before exiting.
